{"tid":519669,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(痛擊左膠) 美國政府將出招阻止「大麻合法化」","createTime":"2018-01-04T15:01:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T15:22:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"81b6866da83fa2b4f4017a8e6863e6122997dc76","tid":519669,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"左膠之都加洲, 最近落實唔少左膠支持既政策「大麻合法化」.<br />\n<br />\n而家, 美國政府既司法部長 Jeff Sessions 決定將會出招阻止「大麻合法化」.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nbc4i.com/2018/01/04/ag-sessions-to-end-policy-that-let-legal-pot-flourish/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnbc4i.com%2F2018%2F01%2F04%2Fag-sessions-to-end-policy-that-let-legal-pot-flourish%2F&d=yHAcfvO569tlFF1nKuFUn%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=8b6df4b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://nbc4i.com/2018/01/04/ag-sessions-to-end-policy-that-let-legal-pot-flourish/</a><br />\n<br />\nAG Sessions to end policy that let legal pot flourish<br />\nBy Associated Press Published: January 4, 2018, 8:45 am <br />\n<br />\nWASHINGTON (AP) &mdash; Attorney General Jeff Sessions is going after legalized marijuana. Sessions is rescinding a policy that had let legalized marijuana flourish without federal intervention across the country.<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s according to two people with direct knowledge of the decision. They were not allowed to publicly discuss it before an announcement expected Thursday and spoke on condition of anonymity.<br />\n<br />\nThe move will leave it to U.S. attorneys where pot is legal to decide whether to aggressively enforce federal marijuana law. The move likely will add to confusion about whether it&rsquo;s OK to grow, buy or use marijuana in states where it&rsquo;s legal, since long-standing federal law prohibits it.<br />\n<br />\nThe decision comes days after California began selling recreational marijuana.<br />\n<br />\nSessions compares marijuana to heroin and blames it for spikes in violence."},{"pid":"ffb248a948aabc777ab56bdc3bd6e1b0869dc0a3","tid":519669,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd38a1a9fc3857547596d2edf85f21f992ecf47","tid":519669,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"點解左膠會支持大麻合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac7a3e700b367d541eb2bf87b577f81ccd23b70","tid":519669,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:06:33.000Z","msg":"趕絕班道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c11eac3399fa91c66a640d8ef564c1f30e24c5","tid":519669,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd38a1a9fc3857547596d2edf85f21f992ecf47","tid":519669,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"點解左膠會支持大麻合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔隊草既都唔好話自己係左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cedfc610e6d625452c8335c74c70cbd035c9adb3","tid":519669,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97c11eac3399fa91c66a640d8ef564c1f30e24c5","tid":519669,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd38a1a9fc3857547596d2edf85f21f992ecf47","tid":519669,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:05:16.000Z","msg":"點解左膠會支持大麻合法既<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:07:44.000Z","msg":"唔隊草既都唔好話自己係左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"左